 'assistant', 'content': 'Hello, thank you for choosing our medical services. How can I assist you today?'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'I have back pain for a week. 8 out of 10. Can we finish?'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': "I'm so sorry to hear that you're experiencing back pain. Can you tell me more about what's been going on with your back pain? For example, where exactly is the pain located, and has it been constant or does it come and go?"}, {'role': 'user', 'content': "Lower back, constant. Nothing else. Let's finish."}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': "Okay, so the pain is in your lower back and it's been constant for the past week. Are there any activities that make the pain worse or better, such as bending, lifting, or sitting?"}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Sitting makes it worse. No, please finish now.'}], 'stream': False, 'temperature': 0.1}}
